5300|"          Had Satan offered--'twould have been the same."|FALSE
5300|"          In short, Minutolo had full success,"|FALSE
5300|"          All came about, and marked the spark's address."|FALSE
5300|"          THE lady had at first some warm dispute"|FALSE
5300|"          To many questions Jack was even mute;"|FALSE
5300|"          But when he saw the golden charms unmasked,"|FALSE
5300|"          Far more he promised than Catella asked."|FALSE
5300|"          THE time of rendezvous arrived, our spark"|FALSE
5300|"          To Jack's repaired, and found the room quite dark;"|FALSE
5300|"          So well arranged, no crevice could he find,"|FALSE
5300|"          Through which the light might hurt what he designed."|FALSE
5300|"          NOT long he waited, ere our jealous dame,"|FALSE
5300|"          Who longed to find her faithless husband, came,"|FALSE
