5300|"          Though difficult, our spark succeeded well;"|FALSE
5300|"          No words of mine can Richard's pleasure tell."|FALSE
5300|"          His fav'rite beauteous belle he now possessed,"|FALSE
5300|"          And triumphed where so oft he'd been repressed,"|FALSE
