5300|"          Begone! said she, nor treat me like a child;"|FALSE
5300|"          Stand off!--away!--thy taction is defiled;"|FALSE
5300|"          My tears express an injured woman's grief;"|FALSE
5300|"          No more thy wife I'll be, but seek relief;"|FALSE
5300|"          Return my fortune--go:--thy mistress seek;"|FALSE
5300|"          To be so constant:--How was I so weak?"|FALSE
