5300|"          What impudence!--You mock me too? she cried"|FALSE
5300|"          Let's see, with blushes if his face be dyed?"|FALSE
5300|"          When from his arms she sprang, a window sought;"|FALSE
5300|"          The shutters ope'd, and then a view she caught;"|FALSE
5300|"          Minutolo, her lover! * * * what surprise!"|FALSE
5300|"          Pale, faint, she instant grew, and closed her eyes:"|FALSE
5300|"          Who would have thought, said she, thou wert so base?"|FALSE
