5300|"          Though num'rous aged husbands you might view."|FALSE
5300|"          A NOBLE chapel soon the fathers raised,"|FALSE
5300|"          To which the females ran and highly praised,"|FALSE
5300|"          Surveyed it o'er and confidently thought,"|FALSE
5300|"          'Twas there, of course, salvation should be sought."|FALSE
5300|"          And when their faith had thoroughly been proved,"|FALSE
