5300|"                      ST. JULIAN'S PRAYER"|FALSE
5300|"          TO charms and philters, secret spells and prayers,"|FALSE
5300|"          How many round attribute all their cares!"|FALSE
5300|"          In these howe'er I never can believe,"|FALSE
5300|"          And laugh at follies that so much deceive."|FALSE
5300|"          Yet with the beauteous FAIR, 'tis very true,"|FALSE
5300|"          These WORDS, as SACRED VIRTUES, oft they view;"|FALSE
5300|"          The spell and philter wonders work in love"|FALSE
