5300|"                            FERONDE"|FALSE
5300|"          IN Eastern climes, by means considered new;"|FALSE
5300|"          The Mount's old-man, with terrors would pursue;"|FALSE
5300|"          His large domains howe'er were not the cause,"|FALSE
5300|"          Nor heaps of gold, that gave him such applause,"|FALSE
