5300|"          His country, and to banishment submit,"|FALSE
5300|"          Resolved that he a season would employ,"|FALSE
5300|"          In visiting the site of ancient Troy."|FALSE
5300|"          His comrade, Cymon, with him thither went,"|FALSE
5300|"          To view those ruins, we so oft lament."|FALSE
