5300|"          MUCH praise Aminta from the dame received;"|FALSE
5300|"          Who promised that the conduct, which aggrieved;"|FALSE
5300|"          To Cleon she would mention, as desired,"|FALSE
5300|"          And reprimand him, as the fault required:"|FALSE
5300|"          So well would scold him, that she might be sure,"|FALSE
